@prefix ex: <http://example.org/medical#> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .

### Individuals
ex:Alice rdf:type ex:Person .
ex:Bob rdf:type ex:Person .
ex:Charlie rdf:type ex:Person .
ex:HuntingtonsDisease rdf:type ex:GeneticCondition .

### The Asserted Data Facts
ex:Alice ex:hasParent ex:Bob .
ex:Bob ex:hasSibling ex:Charlie .
ex:Charlie ex:hasDiagnosedCondition ex:HuntingtonsDisease .